{
  "stem": "13313.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he started asking all kinds of questions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "How things were going and-- and-- and this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now you must remember, this is now end of '43 in the height of the occupation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And at that moment, I did not know what happened, how come he-- why he was there and my mother wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I found out later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So before I get to what happened, I just want to recall what happened from my perspective.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So here my father asked how things are.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On the one hand, I got to be very careful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she hadn't reached the-- the height of her-- of intensity yet in her treatment of us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This just grew worse and worse, still at the very beginning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- but we were going to church and saying the prayers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all this came out from our little story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my father was very, very mad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the kind of person.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he went and brought out a [INAUDIBLE], and he said [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to me, read Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Read.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was not supposed to by her and was afraid of what she was going to do when we get home because I was supposed to be a Christian.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And here my father wants me to read.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I hesitate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my father gave me a backhand right then and there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Slap in the face.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My head almost turned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he says, read!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Just I don't want you to forget that you are a Jew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[CRYING] And I read.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was the visit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We never had another visit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't know if it was because of that or was because it became more dangerous.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That is the last-- only-- only visit in September.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
